import { Component, OnInit } from '@angular/core'; import { ActivatedRoute, Router } from '@angular/router'; import { PatientcrudserviceService } from '../../services/patientcrudservice.service'; import { Patient } from '../../interfaces/patient'; @Component({ selector: 'app-view', templateUrl: './view.component.html', styleUrls: ['./view.component.scss'] }) export class ViewComponent { id!: number; patient!: Patient; constructor( public patientService: PatientcrudserviceService, private route: ActivatedRoute, private router: Router ) { } /** * Write code on Method * * @return response() */ ngOnInit(): void { this.id = this.route.snapshot.params['patientId']; this.patientService.getById(this.id).subscribe((data: any)=>{ this.patient = data.data; }); } }
